_sText:
I'm pretty new to creating maps, so this is my first map that I've made. This is a very simple bomb/defuse map that takes place in a small desert village. This is the beta version so i know there will be some mistakes that I've made and will be fixing those in the future. Hope you all enjoy and any feedback is much appreciated. Thanks.
